Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web.workload

Class RandomIPWorkloadGenerator

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web.workload.RandomIPWorkloadGenerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
IWorkloadGenerator
public class RandomIPWorkloadGenerator extends Object implements IWorkloadGenerator
A workload generator, which sets the IPs of the generated sessions in accordance with a specified IPGenerator. It wraps another instance of IWorkloadGenerator, which creates the sessions, and only adds the IPs.

This class is useful when you have a workload generator that does not create IPs (the wrapped generator) and you want to add random IPs to the generated sessions.
Author:
nikolay.grozev
